faa19991e88cbfd624ac9ce4a0ba12e3d7d54f88680b1a0a156a542a45bafe2053d69c6f309327817f7cc74f5765204bbb3c56ff531efd29d8fd6bb682c78598  Fix-CC-logic-in-configure.patch
